      <div>
        <head>TEI organization (1991)</head>
        <figure>
          <graphic url="../images/tei-structure-1991.png" height="90%"/>
        </figure>
        <cb/>
        <p>The ground work of the TEI was undertaken by four <soCalled>working committees</soCalled>
          and two <soCalled>editors</soCalled>: <list>
            <item>Documentation : composed of experts in bibliography and data archives</item>
            <item>Metalanguage : composed of computer scientists </item>
            <item>Text Analysis and Interpretation : composed of theoretical linguists</item>
            <item>Text Representation : ... everyone else </item>
          </list>
        </p>
        <p rend="box">Analysis vs. representation </p>
      </div>

